description: There's no biz like Rosie's Sno Biz! Sweet frozen treats on the California streets are making their way way to you to help bring out the best in the sunny California days. You've never had shaved ice this light and fluffy, or in so many fantastic flavors! So if you need something cool and refreshing that'll soothe your sweet tooth, Rosie's Sno Biz is the perfect truck for you!
name: Rosie's Sno Biz
